subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Who is the founder of Jodhpur?
explanation_en:
Rao Bika is the founder of Jodhpur. He established the Meera State during the 15th century.

question_en: Who founded Mina Pratap Sagar Lake?
question_hi: मिना प्रतप सगार स्पटालक को किसके निवर्षित
explanation_en: Mina Pratap Sagar Lake was built by Rao Raja Mina Pratap Singh in the 16th century. It is a popular water body located in Jaisamand, Udaipur district.
